{"tid":1555192,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"點樣安慰自己樣衰嘅事實？","createTime":"2019-09-09T09:21:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-09T12:45:48.000Z","uid":21826,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"31c3a537b1f3e8d54aa6aaf3eaa3cf426dda241a","tid":1555192,"uid":21826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T09:21:08.000Z","msg":"啱啱影完證件相 一睇 屌 塊面又多油 又大細眼 一邊腮位又突 啲頭髮又成堆草咁 嗰影相佬仲話幾好 心裡面一定喺度笑鳩我<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n原來平時覺得唔靚嘅人 自己原來都樣衰過佢 <br />\n但其實有時又覺得自己照鏡同影相嗰樣唔同 某啲相係幾靚 夠竟呢個係乜現象？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nbetween, 除咗削骨,有冇方法可以解決腮骨突?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"615ee20364c3683b58679f6c3d2406326b0109a9","tid":1555192,"uid":76697,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T09:22:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cba64f7c7631052c65ec4ad1e672ff76a8206a14","tid":1555192,"uid":21826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"615ee20364c3683b58679f6c3d2406326b0109a9","tid":1555192,"uid":76697,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T09:22:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T09:23:03.000Z","msg":"你有琪琪了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96a48cef260e0c74a02459def48b04e664f2485c","tid":1555192,"uid":49270,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T09:23:11.000Z","msg":"鑽研一樣技能並練至爐火純青<br />\n對樣無幫助<br />\n但最起碼其他人唔會介意你樣衰先<br />\n反而會崇拜你樂意同你做朋友"},{"pid":"44b3fa1109d70077339efa9ffd8e42a2a605c61e","tid":1555192,"uid":158635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T09:24:00.000Z","msg":"試下shading重手啲？"},{"pid":"d9e68999be575aba2c8ce4089b5a30154de631f6","tid":155519